    "The architectural differences and design philosophies underlying various LLMs could influence how effectively the PIL integrates and functions within these models.",
    "Therefore, while the results obtained from the Mistral LLM are significant, they may not directly translate to other LLMs without adaptations and further testing.",
    "Despite those limitations, our study emphasizes the importance of continued research and development in this field.",
    "Addressing these challenges will not only enhance the practical applicability of PIL-integrated LLMs but also contribute to the broader goal of advancing AI technology in a responsible and inclusive manner.",
    "Future Research DirectionsIn the future, there are several promising avenues for further research: ❼ Cross-Model Applicability: Exploring the integration of the PIL into other LLM architectures to assess its versatility and efficacy across different models."
